": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/81da2f0ccc6d838f25ca1f7078a4c31e?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/81da2f0ccc6d838f25ca1f7078a4c31e?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/81da2f0ccc6d838f25ca1f7078a4c31e?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1518320967, "last_modified": 1518320967}, "last_reply_by": "kios", "last_touched": 1650048111, "title": "第三次看 Rust，感觉又快要放弃了😥", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/847187", "created": 1650015047, "deleted": 0, "content": "如题，各位是怎么坚持的，取点经，谢", "content_rendered": "<p>如题，各位是怎么坚持的，取点经，谢</p>\n", "last_modified": 1650015047, "replies": 54, "id": 847187}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_large.png?m=1649311216", "name": "programmer", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_normal.png?m=1649311216", "title": "程序员", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer", "topics": 48307, "footer": "", "header": "While code monkeys are not eating bananas, they're coding.", "title_alternative": "Programmer", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1649311216", "stars": 7780, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 300, "parent_node_name": "computer"}, "member": {"id": 2368, "username": "isno", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/isno", "website": "", "twitter": "", "psn": "", "github": "", "btc": "", "location": "", "tagline": "我就是我，不一样的烟火", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/466a/ccba/2368_mini.png?m=1650024398", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/466a/ccba/2368_normal.png?m=1650024398", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/466a/ccba/2368_large.png?m=1650024398", "created": 1287133709, "last_modified": 1650024398}, "last_reply_by": "isno", "last_touched": 1650071055, "title": "￥ 2890 人民币，买了 5 台腾讯轻量云服务器", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/847223", "created": 1650025369, "deleted": 0, "content": "腾云有个虎年回馈活动， 最长可以买五年。\r\n\r\n我买了 5 台， 共￥ 2890 元， 时间 5 年。\r\n\r\n\r\n三台 2c4G ， 一台 4c8g ， 一台 2c2g 。 轻量云没办法组私有子网，不过关系不大。\r\n\r\n#### 服务器的用途\r\n\r\n2c4g 用了一台装了 GitLab 。 把个人的项目管理起来，业余的项目看起来正规了\r\n\r\n\r\n2c4g 用了两台做了业务 Server 和 Job\r\n\r\n4c8g 的一台用作 DB Server ，装了 MongoDB 和 Elasticsearch\r\n\r\n\r\n以我的经验，以上的配置可以支撑 2000~3000 的 QPS 并发，理论上可以支持百万 DAU 的用户，后面努力找点场景证明下轻量云是否拉胯\r\n\r\n剩下的一台 2c2g\r\n\r\n装了小程序编译器，用来自动编译和发布小程序。。\r\n\r\n\r\n五年期，已经过了两天了，给自己点压力，争取快速把服务器资源利用起来", "content_rendered": "<p>腾云有个虎年回馈活动， 最长可以买五年。</p>\n<p>我买了 5 台， 共￥ 2890 元， 时间 5 年。</p>\n<p>三台 2c4G ， 一台 4c8g ， 一台 2c2g 。 轻量云没办法组私有子网，不过关系不大。</p>\n<h4>服务器的用途</h4>\n<p>2c4g 用了一台装了 GitLab 。 把个人的项目管理起来，业余的项目看起来正规了</p>\n<p>2c4g 用了两台做了业务 Server 和 Job</p>\n<p>4c8g 的一台用作 DB Server ，装了 MongoDB 和 Elasticsearch</p>\n<p>以我的经验，以上的配置可以支撑 2000~3000 的 QPS 并发，理论上可以支持百万 DAU 的用户，后面努力找点场景证明下轻量云是否拉胯</p>\n<p>剩下的一台 2c2g</p>\n<p>装了小程序编译器，用来自动编译和发布小程序。。</p>\n<p>五年期，已经过了两天了，给自己点压力，争取快速把服务器资源利用起来</p>\n", "last_modified": 1650025473, "replies": 37, "id": 847223}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c9e1/074f/104_large.png?m=1647188862", "name": "cloud", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c9e1/074f/104_normal.png?m=1647188862", "title": "云计算", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/cloud", "topics": 4668, "footer": "", "header": "关于云计算技术和平台的综合讨论区。", "title_alternative": "Cloud Computing", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c9e1/074f/104_mini.png?m=1647188862", "stars": 2805, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 104, "parent_node_name": "webmaster"}, "member": {"id": 242537, "username": "shallwei", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/shallwei", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/456c315b72d7290ef71ff943ee2741c7?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/456c315b72d7290ef71ff943ee2741c7?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/456c315b72d7290ef71ff943ee2741c7?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1500522159, "last_modified": 1500522159}, "last_reply_by": "keven1024", "last_touched": 1650055774, "title": "腾讯云香港 两个月被封了 2 次 443，是什么问题？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/847190", "created": 1650015491, "deleted": 0, "content": "2020 年从阿里云转腾讯云的，\r\n平时就看看 youtube ，3 月开始被封了 2 次 443.\r\n域名是实名，未备案难道 443 都要备案吗？还是 vmess 和 trojan 能被识别。\r\n问题是我就看看 youtube 一些国外科技视频。不涉及敏感话题\r\n第一次发工单还帮忙换了 ip ，现在只能自己换好像换 ip 只能换 1 次。\r\n关键续费到年底了不然真的蛋疼啊", "content_rendered": "<p>2020 年从阿里云转腾讯云的，\n平时就看看 youtube ，3 月开始被封了 2 次 443.\n域名是实名，未备案难道 443 都要备案吗？还是 vmess 和 trojan 能被识别。\n问题是我就看看 youtube 一些国外科技视频。不涉及敏感话题\n第一次发工单还帮忙换了 ip ，现在只能自己换好像换 ip 只能换 1 次。\n关键续费到年底了不然真的蛋疼啊</p>\n", "last_modified": 1650015491, "replies": 33, "id": 847190}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_large.png?m=1649311216", "name": "programmer", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_normal.png?m=1649311216", "title": "程序员", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer", "topics": 48307, "footer": "", "header": "While code monkeys are not eating bananas, they're coding.", "title_alternative": "Programmer", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1649311216", "stars": 7780, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 300, "parent_node_name": "computer"}, "member": {"id": 522487, "username": "theklf4", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/theklf4", "website": null, "twitter": "", "psn": "", "github": "", "btc": "", "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/4992f9ff63c26b4694fd1d2ca4e805e5?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/4992f9ff63c26b4694fd1d2ca4e805e5?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/4992f9ff63c26b4694fd1d2ca4e805e5?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1607186074, "last_modified": 1648804125}, "last_reply_by": "aylmer", "last_touched": 1650078487, "title": "base64 编码图片一般会使体积变大多少？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/847238", "created": 1650027925, "deleted": 0, "content": "客户要求把用户上传的 8~9MB 照片全部 base64 保存进数据库防止被传马，API 直接返回 base64 ，给他解释 base64 会让图片变大他理解不了", "content_rendered": "<p>客户要求把用户上传的 8~9MB 照片全部 base64 保存进数据库防止被传马，API 直接返回 base64 ，给他解释 base64 会让图片变大他理解不了</p>\n", "last_modified": 1650027925, "replies": 33, "id": 847238}]